  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Temporal Critical Flows \u2014 Overview",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 11,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "\n**Local OSS view of reference \"OSS critical-path\" dashboard.**\nSource dashboards live in `ref/`; mapping rationale in `internal notes`.\n\nThis stack monitors the **three critical flows** worth watching:\n\n1. **Starting / Signaling** \u2014 `StartWorkflowExecution`, `SignalWorkflowExecution` (customer API creating/modifying workflow state). SLO p99 < 200ms.\n2. **Workflow Progress** \u2014 workers polling (`PollWorkflowTaskQueue`, `PollActivityTaskQueue`) and completing work (`Respond*`).\n3. **Task Processing** \u2014 Temporal's engine processing background tasks (`TransferActive`, `TimerActive`) to generate work for pollers.\n\nUse the **Critical Flows** dropdown (top-left) to drill into each flow + Worker Tuning.\n\n> **OSS vs Cloud parity gaps (intentionally not shown):** AlertManager `ALERTS` (no alerting wired locally), k8s pod CPU-%-of-request (no k8s), storage-engine panels (internal storage layer \u2014 this demo runs **Postgres**, so storage collapses to the persistence API layer), per-namespace breakdowns (`perNamespaceScope` not set), and `service_latency` (no OSS equivalent \u2014 Progress latency below includes worker time). Server metrics use **bare names** (no `temporal_` prefix).\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Frontend \u2014 Critical Operations",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 11
      },
      "id": 2,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Critical Frontend RPS by Operation",
      "description": "",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "id": 3,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (operation) (rate(service_requests{operation=~\"StartWorkflowExecution|SignalWorkflowExecution|SignalWithStartWorkflowExecution|RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|PollWorkflowTaskQueue|PollActivityTaskQueue\"}[$rate]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        }
      ]
    },
